org.pikater.core.options

Class SlotsHelper

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.pikater.core.options.SlotsHelper

  • public abstract class SlotsHelper
extends java.lang.Object
    Abstract class which helps with the definition of slots in the new Box. Each Box contains a ontology, by this type of ontology you can choose the right slot definition
